'''英國港僑協會'''（{{lang|en|Hongkongers in Britain}}，簡稱：{{lang|en|HKB}}）是一個[[港籍英國人|居英港人]]僑務型團體，協會成立目的是為香港人提供一個互相支持的平台，讓他們在英國重建生活，旨在團結在英國的香港人，並與國際香港人社群建立連結。協助香港人既保留獨特文化，同時也融入英國的社區。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.voanews.com/europe/hong-kongers-britain-organize-support-thousands-newcomers|title=Hong Kongers in Britain Organize Support for Thousands of Newcomers {{!}} Voice of America - English|publisher=[[Voice_of_America|Voice of America]]|accessdate=2021-03-12|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410212333/https://www.voanews.com/europe/hong-kongers-britain-organize-support-thousands-newcomers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/31/britain-launches-new-visa-for-millions-of-hongkongers-fleeing-chinas-crackdown|title=Britain launches new visa for millions of Hongkongers fleeing China's crackdown|publisher=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2021-03-12|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430052308/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/31/britain-launches-new-visa-for-millions-of-hongkongers-fleeing-chinas-crackdown|dead-url=no}}</ref>

